node.text:
Checkered flag at the @totalenergies24hoursofspa: After starting from P54, Audi Sport Team WRT, with Audi Sport drivers @kelvinvanderlinde, @dries_vanthoor1 and @charlesweerts in the #32 Audi R8 LMS, fought their way through the pack to finish runner-up after 24 hours of hard racing. 

All four of our Audi Sport teams finished within the top ten: P4 Audi Sport Team WRT #37, P6 Audi Sport Team Saintéloc #25 and P9 Audi Sport Team Attempto #66.

Well done to our teams and customers for competing in this year's endurance classic at @circuit_spa_francorchamps!
